title: It is an (invertible) list of lists.
pid: 635e8e0f-cfda-49f3-b39c-5ea7573c5c9b
body: |2-
  as a tree where generation 1 is the other people,
  and generation 2 is the ideas,
  (The inversion might be incomplete in either direction --
  full set of parents becomes an incomplete set of children.)
